data.clean_description: Delicious maroccan hash mixed with finely toasted tobacco and a variety of high quality skunk. Rolled the danish way. Rolling papers used are with natural gum and no bleech. This little beast wont couchlock you , it s brilliant for daytime smokes , brings that pleasant sensation that brings a big smile to your face through out the day.
data.name: "1 x Pre-Rolled Joint, ""The Wizard"", 50/50 Skunk Ha"
